commit.message: Bumped patch version
Minor readability improvement to scenarios acceptance test
Improved validation of scenario set and reset so that a 422 is returned instead of quietly accepting when an attempt it made to set a scenario to a non-existent state
Improved validation of scenario set and reset so that a 404 is returned when the scenario doesn't exist instead of a 500
Fixed #1854 - unintended removal of name field on scenarios
Closes #1721, closes #1079; Added ability to set and reset a single scenario's state
Added localRelease build task
Bumped minor version
Removed docs-v2 entries from bump version tasks in build
